Keeping you informed and advocating for change! 💪 🎉
NEW AND AVAILABLE NOW!

MPMB Roundtable Series - Utilizing Dental Representatives

Dr. Rob and Tracy Thorup, President and CEO of My Practice My Business, host a roundtable discussion with four experienced Dental Representatives, delving into their perspectives and discussing their insights on dental sales. Watch it HERE!
NEW PODCAST EPISODE 
Dental offices are not profitable by procedure, so hygienist have to work extra hard to make up for lost revenue. It's no wonder hygienists are burned out... But is there something dentists can do to reverse this problem.
Listen to podcast episode 164; The Hygienist Perspective and subscribe to the channel HERE.
EVENT HIGHLIGHTS
Essential Front Office Training Highlight
We recently welcomed dental teams nationwide for our latest MPMB training. Teams from California, Idaho, and Florida joined us at our office in South Jordan, Utah.
Investing in your team is an investment in your success! With the right training, you can empower your team greatness. Register for future events HERE.
TESTIMONIAL
🌟SUCCESS STORY🌟
Dr. Jenson shares why training with My Practice My Business has been one of the best things he's done for his career! Is your dental practice struggling with profitability? Our training can change that.
📖 Submit your story here for a chance to win $100!
SAVE THE DATE
September 4th Intro Course & Sneak Peak
Are you stuck writing off your hard work or being told to drop PPOs completely in order to be profitable?
There is a better way! Watch a free Sneak Peak of our training here and register for a FREE into course. 
Help your practice work harder not smarter- Reserve your spot HERE.
